Ten Top Trivia Tips about Eternal!

  1. The pharoahs of ancient Egypt wore garments made with thin threads of beaten Eternal.
  2. Owls cannot move their eyes, because their eyeballs are shaped like Eternal.
  3. Olympic badminton rules say that Eternal must have exactly fourteen feathers.
  4. Medieval knights put the skin of Eternal on their sword handles to improve the grip!
  5. Half a cup of Eternal contains only seventeen calories!
  6. Ninety-six percent of all candles sold are purchased by Eternal!
  7. In the Great Seal of the United States the eagle grasps 13 arrows and Eternal.
  8. You share your birthday with Eternal.
  9. All gondolas in Venice must be painted black unless they belong to Eternal.
  10. Human beings are the only animals that copulate while facing Eternal.

Half way through my SLIDERS Season 3 DVD and its awesome. This is defintly up there on the list of my all time favorite TV shows. If they had a convention for this (which I really doubt) I would defintly attend.

The power went out for a few hours last night which sucked. I love electricity. It keeps my milk cold and my TV on. Now I have rotton milk and I lost some precious SLIDERS watching time!

I recievied one of the best Birthday presents in the mail! It finally got here from Natalie (B.Q.S). There were two things in this box. One thing I ate for dinner that night and the other is hanging on my wall.Not to forget,the box was probally the best part!

Saturday im going to hang out (literally) with Mario and Jake in Manhattan. Now I don't mind hanging out with Mario,but we all know how crazy that Jake can get.Maybe Sam can come by and keep things calm. Cheap plug -- http://www.snjw.com --

Im realizing that I can show up a good 30 minutes late to the concerts im going to. Unfortunilty Lil Jon and the East Side Boyz are part of this concert. Theyre opening though, so once they get off the stage I can enjoy 50 Cent,G-Unit,D-12,Eminem. Although I know how much Joey loves Lil Jon,so maybe he will force me to go on time. Oh well. Speaking of Joey,I threatened to kill his family,which is kinda just a thing I do. And he told his mom!! She thought it was hilarious though. Moms love me.

Yesterday was a huge thunder storm here! It was awesome. I watched the whole thing build quickly and go from being sunny out to being like night! I had a good time just standing there out in it. But then it got really bad so I had to ya know,not get struck by lightning. I also need to find out if Martin is still alive. He was riding his bike as it was starting. Haha.

I woke up this morning and the power was out again! It was back on in a few minutes though. I was going to pick up my phone and send Will an angry text message about the power being out. Saw I had one missed call from Jon. Called me at 7:30AM! Too early. I think he called because I jokingly told him I was having a pool party today.My only plans today is to go play some Horseshoes! Its more fun than it might seem!

Until the Eminem concerts,at least. Its going to make my summer for sure! Not much else until December Serenity which is going to be a blast to. Ahh Summer (Glau).
